title: Factbox: Reaction as UK PM Johnson moved to intensive care
description: British Prime Minister Boris Johnson was moved to intensive care on Monday after his coronavirus symptoms worsened and he has asked Foreign Secretary Dominic Raab to deputize, Downing Street said.
content:
